snippet.textDisplay:
When i just saw the title of the track and found Aamir Zaki's name in it, i was damn sure that this will be the best of the season and yes it is the best track till now, Aamir Zaki is indeed a Legend. Whenever he played his chords he always indulged in it totally. 
Apart from that, i never knew that Jaffer is so good in playing guitar too. And what a beautiful voice Akbar ali has, just sweet as honey.
Javed bashir is a person who hardly disappoints, or i would say never disappoints. He is absolutely a great singer though!
A very beautiful arrangement altogether! And yes i felt a bit Rohail hyatt's touch in this jaffer zaidi's composition.
Well done Jaffer, u always do justice for being a son of a legendary singer(Madam nayyara noor).
#BestOneSoFar #CS10
